# `@expressthat-auth/{{name}}`

A C# .NET 10 class library workspace package.

## Adding dependencies

To depend on another C# workspace package, add it to `package.json`:

```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "@expressthat-auth/other-lib": "workspace:*"
  }
}
```

Run `pnpm install` – pnpm will symlink the package into
`node_modules/@expressthat-auth/other-lib`, and `{{pascalCase name}}.csproj`
will automatically pick it up as a `ProjectReference` via the glob in its
`ItemGroup`.

## Consuming this package

In the consuming app's `package.json`, add:

```json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "@expressthat-auth/{{name}}": "workspace:*"
  }
}
```

Run `pnpm install` and the consuming project's `ProjectReference` glob will
automatically discover `{{pascalCase name}}.csproj`.
